    "text": "Healthcare Enrollment Reform Modernization and Navigation Act or the HERMAN Act\n\nThis bill establishes and otherwise modifies requirements relating to coordinated coverage between employer health insurance and Medicare.\n\nSpecifically, the bill prohibits employer-sponsored health plans for certain smaller employers from reducing benefits for employees who are eligible for Medicare but have not yet enrolled."
